import{_ as e,o as t,c as a,b as o}from"./app-a6eacc5a.js";const s={},r=o('<h1 id="application-software" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#application-software" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Application Software</h1><p>Application software is <em>a type of</em> software that provides specific functionality to users, <em><code>rather</code> than</em> performing general tasks. It is designed to <code>meet</code> <em>the needs of</em> individual users or organizations and can be used for <em>a wide range of</em> purposes, such as word processing, data analysis, gaming, communication, and more.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentences:</strong></p><p>应用程序软件是一种向用户提供特定功能的软件，而不是执行一般任务。 它专为满足个人用户或组织的需求而设计，可用于广泛的用途，例如文字处理、数据分析、游戏、通信等。</p><p><strong>phrases:</strong></p><p>a type of -&gt; 一种：用于表示某种类别或种类的事物；一种类型的；一种型号的；<br> rather than -&gt; 而不是<br> a wide range of -&gt; 广泛的范围：涵盖很多种类或数量的事物。<br> the needs of -&gt; ......的需求：指某人或某事所需要的东西或条件。</p><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>rather<br><code>英: [ˈrɑːðə(r)] 美: [ˈræðər]</code></p><blockquote><p>adv. 而是；稍微；（常用于表示轻微的批评、失望或惊讶）相当；更准确地说<br> int. 表示同意某人的提议</p></blockquote><p>meet<br><code>英: [miːt] 美: [mit]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 满足；迎接；遇见；相遇 n. 运动会；体育比赛；猎狐运动（现在于英国用狗猎狐属违法行为） adj. 适合的</p></blockquote></details><p>Some common types of application software include:</p><ul><li><p>Desktop applications: These are programs that run on a user&#39;s computer and are typically installed locally. Examples include Microsoft Office Suite, Adobe Creative Suite, and Google Chrome.</p></li><li><p>Mobile applications: These are programs that run on smartphones and <code>tablets</code> and are typically downloaded from app stores. Examples include Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp.</p></li><li><p>Web applications: These are programs that run in a web browser and are accessed through the internet. Examples include online banking systems, e-<code>commerce</code> sites, and social media platforms.</p></li></ul><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentences:</strong><br> 一些常见类型的应用软件包括：</p><ul><li>桌面应用程序: 这些程序运行在用户的计算机上，通常安装在本地。例如，Microsoft Office Suite、Adobe Creative Suite 和 Google Chrome。</li><li>移动应用程序: 这些程序运行在智能手机和平板电脑上，通常从应用程序商店下载。例如 Facebook、 Instagram 和 WhatsApp。</li><li>Web 应用程序: 这些程序在 Web 浏览器中运行，可以通过互联网访问。例如，在线银行系统、电子商务网站和社交媒体平台。</li></ul><p><strong>words:</strong></p><p>tablet<br><code>英 [ˈtæblət]美 [ˈtæblət]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 药片，片剂；丸；（石头、黏土等制的刻字的）牌，碑，匾；平板电脑；&lt;美&gt; 便笺簿，拍纸簿；&lt;旧&gt; 一块肥皂；（单线）路牌；檐板；&lt;苏格兰&gt; 乳脂软糖；（计算机的）输入板，手写板</p></blockquote><p>commerce<br><code>英 [ˈkɒmɜːs] 美 [ˈkɑːmɜːrs]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 贸易，商业；&lt;旧&gt;社交，交往；&lt;旧&gt;性交</p></blockquote></details><p>Application software is developed using programming languages such as C++, Java, Python, and JavaScript, and can be created by individuals or companies. It is often tested and updated regularly to ensure it continues to function properly and meets the needs of its users.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentences:</strong></p><p>应用软件使用诸如C++、Java、Python和JavaScript等编程语言进行开发，可以由个人或公司创建。它经常经过测试并定期更新，以确保其继续正常运行并满足用户的需求。</p></details>',8),n=[r];function i(p,c){return t(),a("div",null,n)}const d=e(s,[["render",i],["__file","10-application-software.html.vue"]]);export{d as default};
